  "description": "Secure-by-design and flexible Unix socket proxy. Built in memory-safe Go with zero dependencies, no shell or interpreter required in containers. A modern alternative to tecnativa/docker-socket-proxy and linuxserver/docker-socket-proxy, with powerful regex-based configuration.",
